## Paso 1 · Imagen inicial / Hero shot

**Tool**:

**Prompt**:

```
Create a high-quality {{PRODUCT_TYPE}} image using the uploaded product photo.
Place the product floating in the center of the frame with a slight natural tilt.
Use clean, soft studio lighting with subtle highlights and shadows.
Keep all original label details sharp and readable.

STYLE:
• {{STYLE_REFERENCE}}
• Clean color separation
• Slight vignette but no gradients

BACKGROUND:
• {{BACKGROUND_COLOR}}
• No reflections, no textures

FRAMING:
• {{ASPECT_RATIO}}
• Product centered
• Enough margins for later motion-tracking

OUTPUT:
• High-resolution still image
• {{BACKGROUND_COLOR}} background for easy masking
• Maintain the exact shape, colors, and proportions of the uploaded product image
```

