## Paso 3 · Transición (img→video)

**Tool**:

**Prompt**:

```
Create a dynamic transition from the mid-spin frame to the final ingredient-burst frame.
Begin with the product tilted left in mid-rotation on a {{BACKGROUND_COLOR}} background.
As the rotation continues, introduce {{INGREDIENT}} pieces gradually entering the frame.
Increase the number of floating {{INGREDIENT}} elements as the motion progresses.
Add a high-energy liquid splash emerging from behind the product.
All elements must look sharp and suspended in high-speed motion.
Ensure the product stays well-lit, well-centered, and unobstructed.
Background stays {{BACKGROUND_COLOR}} with no additional effects.
End in the fully exploded ingredient-burst composition.
```

**Clip elegido**: `05-clips/selects/transition-<v>.mp4`

