## Glosario de variables

- `{{PRODUCT_TYPE}}`: ej. "beverage can", "bottle", "snack pack"
- `{{INGREDIENT}}`: ej. "blueberries", "ice cubes", "mint leaves"
- `{{STYLE_REFERENCE}}`: ej. "modern DTC beverage ads", "Apple product launch", "Y2K nostalgia"
- `{{BACKGROUND_COLOR}}`: ej. "pure solid black (#000000)", "pastel pink (#FFD6E0)"
- `{{ASPECT_RATIO}}`: "full vertical frame (9:16)", "square (1:1)", "horizontal (16:9)"
